	</div>

    <div class="inner-panel_lg_holder">
      <h2>Profile information</h2>
        <div class="inner-panel_lg">
          <div id="tabx" class="clearfix">
            <div class="form00 fix-ie-preface">
              <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Vivamus eros dui, ornare id molestie vel, placerat id odio.
              Nam non lorem id mauris rutrum euismod vel at est. Ut at imperdiet eros. Suspendisse iaculis faucibus volutpat.
